It feels that our hard work, the good & bad times and all the ups and downs have paid off.

We'd like to say thank you to our beloved and gorgeous lecturer ( @vickyhombing ) and assistant lecturer ( @karina_septiani ) for teaching and guiding us all the way through. You're Next is a 2011 American independent home invasion slasher film directed by Adam Wingard & written by Simon Barrett. 
The film had its world premiere at the 2011 Toronto International Film Festival Midnight Madness program. The film was released on August 23, 2013, in the United States to positive reviews and grossed over $26 million at the box office. üé•
